---
import MLabel from "@/components/ui/MLabel.vue";
---

<section class="paths-lede">
	<MLabel tone="spruce">
		<span class="paths-lede__dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
		§00 · Why paths
	</MLabel>
	<h1 class="paths-lede__title">
		A curriculum is a promise <span class="paths-lede__title-soft">that the order matters.</span>
	</h1>
	<p class="paths-lede__body">
		Picking lessons one at a time is fine for browsing. Picking them in the
		right order is how you actually become competent at the thing. Each path
		here was built by someone who teaches this for a living and watched, in
		detail, where students get stuck.
	</p>
</section>

<style>
	.paths-lede {
		padding: 3.25rem 2.5rem 2.25rem;
		border-bottom: 1px solid var(--editorial-hairline);
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 1.125rem;
	}

	.paths-lede__dot {
		width: 6px;
		height: 6px;
		border-radius: 50%;
		background: var(--editorial-spruce);
	}

	.paths-lede__title {
		font-family: var(--font-instrument-serif), serif;
		font-style: italic;
		font-weight: 400;
		font-size: clamp(2.75rem, 6vw, 5.25rem);
		line-height: 0.94;
		letter-spacing: -0.025em;
		color: var(--editorial-ink);
		margin: 0;
		max-width: 70rem;
		text-wrap: balance;
	}

	.paths-lede__title-soft {
		font-style: normal;
		font-family: var(--font-inter-tight), sans-serif;
		font-size: 0.72em;
		font-weight: 400;
		color: var(--editorial-ink-soft);
	}

	.paths-lede__body {
		font-family: var(--font-inter-tight), sans-serif;
		font-size: 1.1875rem;
		line-height: 1.5;
		color: var(--editorial-ink-soft);
		margin: 0;
		max-width: 55rem;
		text-wrap: pretty;
	}

	@media (max-width: 720px) {
		.paths-lede { padding: 2.25rem 1.25rem 1.5rem; }
	}
</style>
